title: Minuteful - Kidney Test
description:
Minuteful Kidney is an FDA-cleared home urine test that allows you to check your kidney health using your smartphone.

*This app can only be used in the US with the designated Minuteful - Kidney Test kit*

Using the Minuteful - Kidney Test app and kit, you can easily test anytime, anywhere in just five minutes and get clinical-grade results on the spot.

The app will guide you through the testing process step-by-step, and the results will be available for you to share with your doctor and help you take charge of your health.

The Minuteful - Kidney Test is HIPAA compliant.
